    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p> <p>Add the<strong> wheat berries</strong> to a large pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> (the same as you would for pasta)</p> <p>Cook over a high heat for 10 min</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/citrus-chicken-and-warm-wheat-berry-salad/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>baby plum tomatoes</strong> in half</p> <p>Slice the <strong>radishes</strong> finely into rounds</p> <p>Chop the <strong>green beans</strong> in half</p> <p>Trim, then finely&nbsp;slice the <strong>spring onions</strong>&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/citrus-chicken-and-warm-wheat-berry-salad/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>wheat berries</strong> have been cooking for 10 min, add the<strong> chopped green beans</strong> and cook for a further 3-4 min or until everything is tender&nbsp;</p> <p>When the<strong> beans</strong> are tender, drain and return to the pot</p> <p>Add the <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>radishes</strong> and<strong> spring onions</strong>&nbsp;to the drained<strong> wheat berries</strong> and set aside&nbsp;</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/citrus-chicken-and-warm-wheat-berry-salad/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, zest&nbsp;the <strong>lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into a bowl</p> <p>Place your hand flat onto the <strong>chicken breast<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p> <p>Slice in half as if you were cutting a burger bun, so you are left with two thinner pieces</p> <p>Add the <strong>sliced chicken</strong> to the bowl of <strong>lemon zest</strong> with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper&nbsp;</strong></p> <p>Give everything a good old mix up</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/citrus-chicken-and-warm-wheat-berry-salad/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat and once hot, add the <strong>chicken</strong> to the pan with any remaining oil and lemon zest</p> <p>Cook for 6-8 min, turning once halfway or until cooked through &ndash; this is your<strong> citrus chicken</strong></p> <p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>capers</strong> finely</p> <p>Chop the <strong>chives</strong> and <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/citrus-chicken-and-warm-wheat-berry-salad/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked through, transfer it to a board to rest</p> <p>Return the pan to a very low heat and add 40g <span class=\"text-danger\">[80g]</span> <strong>butter</strong>&nbsp;</p> <p>Cook for 30 sec-1 min or until melted&nbsp;</p> <p>Add the <strong>chopped capers</strong> and the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; this is your <strong>caper butter dressing&nbsp;</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/citrus-chicken-and-warm-wheat-berry-salad/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>rested chicken</strong></p> <p>Add the <strong>caper butter dressing</strong> to the <strong>wheat berries</strong> with the <strong>chopped herbs</strong> and a very generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>&nbsp;</p> <p>Give everything a good mix up &ndash; this is your <strong>wheat berry salad</strong>&nbsp;</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/citrus-chicken-and-warm-wheat-berry-salad/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Cut the remaining<strong> lemon</strong> into wedges&nbsp;</p> <p>Serve the <strong>sliced citrus chicken</strong> over the<strong> wheat berry salad</strong>&nbsp;</p> <p>Season with a generous grind of<strong>&nbsp;black pepper </strong>and garnish with a<strong> lemon wedge</strong></p> <p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
